snippet.title: Cinematic：“We Ride"
snippet.description:
The thorn withered… The White Hawk perished…
All rendered by the hand of evil…
It's strong, tough, and inevitable…
Those dreadful puppets…
That thirsty army…
They bring about an age of blade and flame.
So we... will turn to dust, with supreme pride in name.
